title: People reveal their VERY embarrassing photos
text: Share this article Share This hefty fellow seems amused by his own bowl haircut and doesn't appear to be too bothered by his eye patch either This teen opted for a bold look with her fringed mullet and oversized glasses combo This young woman looked like she was on her way to a Seventies disco, which she possibly was This precocious lady seems super confident in her coordinated look and sassy pose One can only assume this photo was taken before There's Something About Mary was released This kid was understandably delighted by his flamboyant look - and you can bet the photographer didn't forget him in a hurry This young man was clearly proud of his rapidly developing facial hair - not to mention his mullet This young lady opted for oversized glasses teamed with a gravity-defying fringe This child opted for a somewhat Victorian look, but with a cartoon character twist The likelihood of this photo having been taken in the Eighties is very, very high Yet another young woman had to sport orthodontic headgear during her teens Given the very large collars and those sideburns, writing the date on this photo was probably unnecessary This photo is bound to make even the most cold-hearted person raise a smile This curly-haired teen looks as though she could pass for someone twice her age Share or comment on this article Most watched News videos
